These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, photography, puzzles, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, western, adventure, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, snowmobile, train
1. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the train is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | card-games      | fishing | photography | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | disaster  | western   | time-travel    |
| Transport     | motorbike     | snowmobile    | train    | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, baking, traveling, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, argentine, malaysian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, train, subway
1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the argentine##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the spanish##1
7. the brazilian is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is baking##2
8. the malaysian is between the spanish and the person who's hobby is traveling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | gardening | traveling   | baking | board-games  |
| Nationality   | argentine     | brazilian | malaysian  | spanish |
| Transport     | subway        | train  | tram    | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, eggplant, pomegranate, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, japanese, turkish, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, airplane, quad-bike
1. the dutch is between the person eating banana and the person eating lettuce##2
2. the japanese is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person eating lettuce is in an odd position##4
6. the turkish is between the person eating eggplant and the polish##2
7. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | banana | eggplant   | lettuce     | pomegranate     |
| Nationality   | japanese  | dutch | turkish   | polish  |
| Transport     | quad-bike      | taxi | airplane | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, epic, superhero, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, country, disco, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding, swimming
1. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
2. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
5. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of rock##1
7. the fan of disco is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | western   | superhero     | epic |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | gospel      | rock        | country     |
| Sport         | snowboarding | cricket | swimming | ice-hockey   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, mexican, spanish, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding, badminton, cycling
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bike, train
1. the argentine is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the spanish is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
7. the mexican is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
9. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | british   | argentine   | spanish | mexican |
| Sport         | skateboarding      | cycling | biathlon      | badminton |
| Transport     | boat | airplane        | train       | bike  |

