.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cranberry, spinach, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, drawing, dancing, reading
4 different pets are kept: pony, bird, hedgehog, lizard
1. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating apple is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | spinach   | apple      | cranberry       | asparagus |
| Hobby   | puzzles | reading | dancing     | drawing |
| Pet     | lizard     | bird  | pony | hedgehog |

