.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, sprite, milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, documentary, crime
4 different pets are kept: hamster, fish, rabbit, lizard
1. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching drama movies##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the person watching crime movies and the owner of the hamster##2
3. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite   | milk          | iced-tea | soy-milk        |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | adventure | crime   | drama     |
| Pet           | hamster | fish         | lizard         | rabbit |

