.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, camping, traveling, dancing
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, doctor, coach, accountant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, soul, jazz, metal
1. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the coach is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the accountant is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of soul is between the freelancer and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the coach##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | magic-tricks      | traveling       | dancing    |
| Job           | doctor  | coach  | accountant | freelancer |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | jazz | soul         | pop    |

