.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, tea, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, dancer, analyst, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, rowing, lacrosse
1. the software-developer is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the software-developer##1
7. the software-developer is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the dancer is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
9. the chef is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | sprite         | juice  | tea     | 7up         |
| Job        | chef | dancer | software-developer | analyst         |
| Sport      | cricket         | rowing  | biathlon   | lacrosse |

