.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, pop, d&b, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, polish, italian
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goldfish, goat
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 2. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 4. the polish is between the fan of pop and the fan of metal##2
 5. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 6. the owner of the goat is the fan of d&b##1
 7. the italian is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
 9. the pakistani is between the fan of rock and the fan of d&b##2
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | d&b    | pop | rock    |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | pakistani  | italian |
| Pet           | goldfish   | goat    | bird        | frog   |

