.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, security-guard, project-manager, social-worker
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese, polish, mexican
1. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
2. the security-guard is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the mexican is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
4. the security-guard is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the journalist##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the security-guard##1
7. the chinese is on the left of the security-guard##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the chinese##3
9. the person drinking water is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | water                | hot-chocolate  | lemonade | sprite   |
| Job           | social-worker | security-guard | journalist   | project-manager |
| Nationality   | chinese         | pakistani     | mexican     | polish |

