.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, mango, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, thriller, documentary
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, folk, trance
1. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the fan of ambient is between the person watching documentary movies and the fan of trance##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | mango    | cabbage  | grapes  | broccoli |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | fantasy | comedy | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | ambient     | trance    | reggae |

