.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, cola, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, indian, spanish, canadian
4 different pets are kept: fish, bird, guinea-pig, lizard
1. the owner of the bird is between the person drinking cola and the japanese##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the spanish is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the indian##1
5. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
7. the japanese is on the left or right of the canadian##3
8. the spanish is the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the canadian is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | cola      | iced-tea  | juice    |
| Nationality   | spanish   | indian | canadian | japanese |
| Pet           | lizard      | guinea-pig       | bird   | fish      |

