.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, filmmaking, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, russian, thai, colombian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, rowing, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's sport is climbing##2
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the colombian is between the person who's sport is climbing and the mexican##2
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the russian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing    | filmmaking | collecting  | card-games  |
| Nationality   | thai | russian       | colombian | mexican |
| Sport         | rowing   | climbing      | basketball | skateboarding       |

