1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
6. the person watching action movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | lemonade | coffee     | sprite    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | action      | crime | scientific |
| Pet           | fish   | chinchilla  | ferret     | mouse |

