The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, snowboarding, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, trike, helicopter
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
