4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
5. the person drinking 7up is between the person driving the taxi and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | 7up     | almond-milk    | sprite        |
| Sport       | snowboarding   | lacrosse | parkour | golf |
| Transport   | helicopter | trike      | taxi    | skateboard   |

