.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, nectarine, strawberry, cucumber
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, woodworking, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, chinchilla, dog
1. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
5. the person eating nectarine is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating onion##1
8. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | strawberry    | nectarine    | onion  | cucumber |
| Hobby   | puzzles | fishing | gardening | woodworking      |
| Pet     | lizard   | hedgehog        | dog   | chinchilla       |

 